vta.core

Compute

Related Doc: package core

class Compute extends Module

Compute.

The compute unit is in charge of the following: - Loading micro-ops from memory (loadUop module) - Loading biases (acc) from memory (tensorAcc module) - Compute ALU instructions (tensorAlu module) - Compute GEMM instructions (tensorGemm module)
